                    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
                      A documentary film that provides a look at the creativity behind everything from toothbrushes to tech gadgets.
                      Watch the complete film <a href="https://objectifiedfilm.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">here</a>. {/* Adjusted color */}
                    </p>
                    <div class="aspect-video bg-gray-100 rounded-md flex items-center justify-center my-8">
