                        Take a look at your current product — is design contributing in an innovative way? Does it make the product
                        useful, understandable, and aesthetic? Is it long-lasting, or will it look outdated or break in a few years?
                      </p>
                      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
                        These are really hard questions to answer. Designers enable you to work within these constraints to create a
