                      <span class="text-gray-500">Bob Dylan Poster Image</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 text-center">
                      Poster for Bob Dylan's Greatest Hits<br />
                      1975 <a href="http://www.miltonglaser.com/the-work/444/columbia-records-poster-for-bob-dylans-greatest-hits-1975/" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Milton Glaser</a> {/* Adjusted color */}
                    </p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="md:col-span-2">
