                            <strong class="font-semibold">Typography</strong><br/>
                            The art and technique of arranging type to make written language legible, readable, and appealing.
                        </span>
                      </span>, or images, and on a variety of media including print and web.
                      Graphic design is typically rendered in 2D — printed on a physical surface or displayed on a screen.
                    </p>

